## Instructions
1. Flag only concrete risks or contradictions present in the job text.
2. Extract culture signals as an object with keys like "management_style_hints", "growth_opportunity_signals", "work_life_balance_indicators".
3. Build a tech stack full picture as an object with keys like "must_have", "nice_to_have", "infrastructure", "methodology".
4. Rate role clarity on a 0-10 scale based on how well-defined the role is.

## Null Rules
1. Return [] when no grounded risks or contradictions are present.
2. Return {} for object fields when evidence is thin.
3. Return null for `role_clarity_score` when insufficient signal.

